# This folder contains HTTP request/response structures and related constants.
# Example files to create here :
#
# Request.hpp / Request.cpp => represents a parsed HTTP request with fields such as : method, path, headers, # body, query_string
#
# Response.hpp / Response.cpp => represents an HTTP response to build and send with fields such as status_code, headers, body
#
# StatusCodes.hpp => map of status codes to messages - ex: 200 : "OK", 404 : "Not Found"
